<body>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    Hey there!
  </p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    Get your <%= @calculations.month %> report on traffic at your restaurant <%= link_to "by clicking here", invoice_url(vid: @calculations.venue.id, months_before: @calculations.months_before) %>.
  </p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    <b>Quick Summary:</b>
    <br><br>
    &#8212; You created <b><%= @calculations.total_purchases_by_charities['Kids Food Basket (local)'] %></b> <a href="http://blog.foodcircles.net/2014/01/08/life-of-a-sack-supper-kids-food-basket/">sack supper(s)</a> for children living in poverty in GR (via Kids' Food Basket) <br><br>
    &#8212; You created <b><%= @calculations.total_purchases_by_charities['World Vision (abroad)'] %></b> day(s) of <a href="http://blog.foodcircles.net/2014/01/08/plumpynut/">plumpy'nut</a> for malnourished children in Niger, West Africa (via World Vision)<br><br>
