  </p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">You can find corresponding group sizes, confirmation codes, and dates in the link above.</p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;"><i>
"#bofo" comes alive to groups when you make it real they're doing something special by eating at your restaurant. The little things you can do (a "thank you", a table tent, etc) matter.</i>
  </p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;"><i>Our promise is this: anything we can do to help you, your staff, or to promote the fact you are a "Buy One, Feed One" establishment, we will. Request anything you need at (616) 61-FOOD-6 or support@joinfoodcircles.org.</i></p>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">
  &#8212; &#8212; FoodCircles
  </p>
